Class AdapterDescriptor.Handler

  • java.lang.Object
    • siminov.web.model.AdapterDescriptor.Handler
  • Enclosing class:
    AdapterDescriptor

    public static class AdapterDescriptor.Handler
extends java.lang.Object
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Web Descriptor Adapter Handler information as per define in WebDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
